banda &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; is a 2003 tamil film directed by t. p. gajendran and produced by p. t. selvakumar . the movie is a remake of the 1998 malayalam movie &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; machan starring mukesh , baiju , jagathy sreekumar and oduvil unnikrishnan which was also remade in telugu as hungama in 2005 and in hindi as housefull 2 in 2012 .